Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.71,0:00:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,流下的泪水早已干枯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对血感到饥渴的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡散发着\N{\fs8}\N{\r}天使柔和羽毛气息飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗太阳不西沉的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,任谁都沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛奇术般的运转
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,见不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,能够拯救我们的神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,人们是疲惫的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,祭坛的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.80,0:01:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,机械梦想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,从黑暗苏醒的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,祭坛的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,螺丝中断的梦想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃自古命运之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管死亡的两名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗圣手为幼婴带来安详
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,墨西哥人那群家伙\N{\fs8}\N{\r}好像自以为已经拿下纽约了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,军队一定会从墨西哥\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不断地偷渡进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能再坐视不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那些人没有什么好失去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们过去的祖先一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界饿肚子的人最强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但是葛奥奈老大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,保护我们父兄\N{\fs8}\N{\r}付出血汗得到的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是光荣男子的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要击垮墨西哥人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以Cosa Nostra之名发誓\N{\fs8}\N{\r}（“Cosa Nostra”意同“黑手党”）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,葛奥奈老大，告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:14.81,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,385)}#08 不可侵犯者 acte Ⅰ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,黑手党不会叫自己黑手党
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,移民到西西里的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,称自己为“Cosa Nostra”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,委托人手中握有着“那个”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有其它选择
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们完成了任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们还没有拿到那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,还没拿到当初说好的合约书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那边我都谈好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,葛奥奈家族的合约书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,终于找到关于索达的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,里面究竟写着什么\N{\fs8}\N{\r}真叫人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沙巴多雷老大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,里卡德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去叫在西西里的\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不可侵犯者（lntoccabile）过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现在马上去叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其它的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果知道了什么再告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫无畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的不可侵犯者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,五年前，你杀了你亲生父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你父亲违反了谦让守则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你只不过是做了理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,继承了最纯正的葛奥奈家血统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孙子希法娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我将你关在西西里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你也毫无怨言遵守了我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,时代变了，实在太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如今能保护黑手党名誉的\N{\fs8}\N{\r}只剩下你一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所有光荣的家族成员\N{\fs8}\N{\r}都在等着看你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,葛奥奈家族所有的力量\N{\fs8}\N{\r}现在都交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,接下它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你杀了你父亲的短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅夺走了你的自由\N{\fs8}\N{\r}还葬送了家族的威信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你，希法娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者…你有听过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者“lntoccabile”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能触碰的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我父亲跟西西里的掌权者很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有一次他带我到西西里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见沙巴多雷老大来见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,希法娜．葛奥奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,世界上最凶残的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,暗杀鲁西欧老大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:11:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很明显地在事前\N{\fs8}\N{\r}就知道老大的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人里面有叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你，里琢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟墨西哥人串通\N{\fs8}\N{\r}出卖了老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快杀了我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,西西里有句名言是“血债血还”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是我找Noir的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一份已经没用的古老合约书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir很想要这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,原因我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！饶了他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,保罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多明尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,方济
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,以圣人为名的三名黑手党成员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在西西里享有盛名的那三人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,赶去见了不可侵犯者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫无畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,听说Noir以这个为条件\N{\fs8}\N{\r}接下了鲁西欧老大的暗杀任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,里琢那小子\N{\fs8}\N{\r}居然找来这种一流的杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把暗杀鲁西欧老大的\N{\fs8}\N{\r}这笔帐算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是身为家族新领导者的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，要我们先动手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们有这东西\N{\fs8}\N{\r}对方一定会主动找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，最好能让对方更容易来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,委托人被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,合约书被希法娜拿走了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,一定错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,希法娜带着那三人\N{\fs8}\N{\r}到新泽西的别墅去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她在等着我们是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,即使赌上荣耀\N{\fs8}\N{\r}也要将Noir处以极刑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是那个人身上的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不可侵犯者“lntoccabile”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我赢不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有她…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只有接受挑战一途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,主述说着万物的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,但是胆敢违抗\N{\fs8}\N{\r}不可侵犯者之愚者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,主一定也会对其唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也不看看自己有几两重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,解决掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,比传闻还要强的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,希法娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你有看到Noir的长相吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没办到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我们失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,脸…有被看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫无畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷优
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:34.50,ED,,0,0,0,,轻轻地被触碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:47.28,ED,,0,0,0,,终于察觉到脸颊的冰冷
